parameters:
\F[nakosu_angry]Nadeshiko: "As I thought... you were lying in
wait... Akane."

\FF[furi_smile]Akane: "You knew and yet you came here... That
takes courage. You're serious, aren't you,
Nadeshiko♪"

\F[nakosu_angry]\FF[furi_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "I'm always serious. I've never lied to
you, Akane!"

\F[nakosu_angry]\FF[furi_smile]\AA[2]Akane: "Even if I try to persuade you, you won't
listen... not the Nadeshiko of now."

\F[nakosu_angry]\FF[furi_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Of course. Because... the Akane of now
isn't the real Akane."

\F[nakosu_angry]\FF[furi_smile]\AA[2]Akane: "Then... maybe I should have everyone
convince you♪ Stubborn Nadeshiko might respond
better to that approach♪"

\FF[yuri_free]Yurika: "Shiratora-san... no, Nadeshiko. We were
wrong. We didn't realize the wonderfulness of
being free like this. This freedom is a reward
from our master♪"

\FF[yuri_free]Yurika: "It's irresistible♪ I want to teach you
this happiness too♪ To become one with our master.
You want to become one with our master too, don't
you, Nadeshiko?"
\F[nakosu_angry]\FF[yuri_free]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "President... I..."

\FF[iruka_free]Iruka: "You should just say you want to if that's
how you really feel♪ Shiratora-san is always so
tsundere. It would be easier if you just admitted
it♪"

\FF[inu_free]Maple: "It's all because my teaching hasn't been
thorough enough, causing trouble for our master～♪
My class only admits free-spirited students! Stiff
Shiratora-san, you better reform quickly♪"
\F[nakosu_trouble]\FF[inu_free]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Senpai... Sensei..."

\FF[ajiri_free]Yui: "People say we're born with roles to play,
but that's nonsense♪ If you're dyed in one single
feeling, nothing is difficult. Just live freely,
that's all there is to it♪"

\FF[sumire_free]Sumire: "Exactly. Shiratora-san, you think too
much♪ From now on, you don't have to think about
anything... You can entrust everything to our
master♪"
\F[nakosu_angry]\FF[sumire_free]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "That's not what freedom is!"

\FF[kikyou_free]Kikyo: "Being stubborn will only wear both you and
our master down. You know that! The answer that
makes everyone happiest is!! For you to join us♪"

\FF[himawari_free]Himawari: "We're all here trying to persuade you,
so be a little more understanding! Having no
allies... that's just too painful, isn't it?"

\FF[syuu_free]Hiiragi: "Nadeshiko-chi, come on. You know what
the right answer is now that it's come to this～?
So there's only one thing to do♪"

\F[nakosu_angry]\FF[himawari_free]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "That's because everyone has turned
into monsters...!"

\FF[ayaka_free]Ayaka: "No, it's just that Nadeshiko hasn't become
as free as us♪ Everyone loves being free, that's
why they've become your enemies."

\FF[ayaka_free]Ayaka: "You too... want to get along with our
master... don't you?"
\FF[ayaka_free]Ayaka: "Or do you... hate our master?"
\F[nakosu_trouble]\FF[ayaka_free]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Hate Akane...? There's no way..."

\F[nakosu_trouble]Nadeshiko: "Enough... enough already! I want to
talk just with you! Akane!!"

\FF[furi_smile]Akane: "Make sure you listen to what everyone has
to say, Nadeshiko."
